CPANPLUS/Shell/Tk version 0.01
==============================

CPANPLUS::Shell::Tk is a graphical user interface for CPANPLUS using Tk.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

  Tk
  Tk::MListbox
  Tk::Pod
  Tk::Splashscreen

